These are visits with extreme long wait time. 
<font color="red" >Investigation needed !</font>

Long wait usually affect customer satisfaction  severely. 

These visits are not used in the calculation of average wait time for the office due to the application of the 3-standard deviation filter.

dashboard_elements.body_text:
These are visits with extreme long service time or preparation time. Investigation recommended ! Long service time could indicate operational improvement opportunity, such as:
- Peer help opportunity
- Training opportunity
- Service design improvement These visits are not used in the calculation of average service time for the office due to the application of the 3-standard deviation filter.

dashboard_elements.body_text:
These are the abck office activities with extreme long time.
<font color="red" >GA Review recommended !</font> 

These back office activities are not used in the calculation of average back office duration time for the office due to the application of the 3-standard deviation filter. If these are legitimate back office activities, the actual time credit for the office may be under reported.
